Recruitment Associate Director- Contracts
1621468,
McCall Limited
Sector: HR & Training
Job Function: Other HR & Training
Job Type: Permanent
Location: Singapore
Role:
Associate Director - Contracts Singapore Salary: Circa $15k pm + guarantee + bonus McCall's client is one of the worlds leading Recruitment Consultancies with offices worldwide and an industry reputation for quality covering nearly every recruitment spectrum. They are currently looking to add to their Senior Management Team by appointing a new Associate Director to look after their Contracts Recruitment Division. This opportunity will see the successful candidate walk into a successful established Division with a remit to grow the business sustainably but quickly across all there established offices in the region. The role will report directly to the COO of the company and provides an excellent career opportunity in a market which is one of the fastest growing in the world.
To be eligible for this outstanding opportunity you will have experience working in a Senior Recruitment Management role in Asia and have a strong understanding of the culture & recruitment practices. Previous experience running Contracts Recruitment Division would also be expected along with a strong management background showing sustained growth.
To apply for this role please email your CV to Peter Mills
Reg No. R EA: 12C5104
Benefits:
Posted: 03.05.2014       Expires: 31.05.2014
